            <h2 class="right-line">Innovative IT solutions for over 10 years</h2>
            <p>After the founding of sbix GmbH in 2001 by Stefan Nesselhauf and its transformation into pixabit GmbH in 2005, in July 2012 <strong>pixabit solutions GmbH</strong> was founded as a spin-off specializing in software development.</p>

            <p>Since that time, 50 permanent employees under the flagship companies <a href="http://www.pixabit-solutions.de/">pixabit solutions GmbH</a> and <a href="http://www.pixabit-interactive.de/">pixabit interactive GmbH</a> (digital brand development and web development), as well as our own teams in Kiev have developed custom software and IT solutions in perfect harmony.</p>

            <p>
