            </p>

            <h3 class="right-line">Stefan Nesselhauf, Managing Director</h3>
            <p>My staff and I are committed to the implementation of client requirements as functional products that save time and money.</p>

            <p>
                I have assisted companies with IT services since 1995, particularly in the areas of software development, SAP, and the administration of heterogeneous UNIX/Windows networks and systems.
            </p>
            <p>
                With the founding of sbix GmbH over 12 years ago, I was able to combine all of my previous activities in UNIX, Windows and SAP, forming the basis for the range of solutions which pixabit solutions GmbH offers today.
            </p>
            <p>
                My experience as an architect and Scrum-certified Product Owner, as well as the collective expertise of our team are at your service for meeting your requirements.
            </p>
            <p>
                Today <strong>pixabit solutions GmbH</strong> brings the widest range of skills under one roof for the purpose of reaching one objective: Software that works for your success.
